 Simply activates something in front of it. 
Can be configured.

block.witherutils.angel.desc:
§9How to use:§r

block.witherutils.anvil.desc:
§9How to Become:§r 
 Place a Vanilla Anvil and right Click it with a SoulOrb. 

 §9How to use:§r 
 Place Ingredients with Right Click. Use the Hammer, to smash it.
block.witherutils.bricks_lava.desc:
§9How to use:§r
 Nothing Special. 
will stop Burning when Rain is gone.

 Crouch and Click will place the Block to the Front. Good for scanning Entities.

Auto LR Clicker with Speed Modifier and Crouching. 
Slot for Items/Tools.
block.witherutils.collector.desc:
§9How to use:§r
Collecting within a Range. Like Magnets do 
Can be configured with a Filter Card. 
Can burn and delete, if overflowing Slots.
block.witherutils.core.desc:

show you the needed Blocks around.
block.witherutils.farmer.desc:
§9How to use:§r
 Needs a Hoe and Seeds. Water is optional. 
Fertilizer Fluid have BoneMeal Effects.
block.witherutils.fisher.desc:
§9How to Place:§r
 Needs Water around. 
 §9How to use:§r
 Needs a Fishing Rod in a Slot. 
Needs Food in a Slot. 
If you enable the AutoFeed Button 
the Fisher looks for Food in 
the Output Slots.
block.witherutils.floodgate.desc:
§9How to use:§r

block.witherutils.floorsensor.desc:

send a Signal to above. 
example: can open Doors or activate RS Stuff.
block.witherutils.greenhouse.desc:
§9How to use:§r

any Aging Progress of Crops. Like Bonemeal
block.witherutils.lava_generator.desc:

Will be burn under Sun or Light 
 and grows faster, when in 
Dark Areas.

Connect Energy Cables to Input/Output.
block.witherutils.rack_case.desc:
§9How to:§r
 This block is used to create a Data Rack. Create a hollow 3x3x3 structure with at least one Rack Controller in the Middle, and one or more Rack Terminals in a face (not edge or corner) of the structure.
block.witherutils.rack_terminal.desc:
§9How to:§r
 This block is the Input and Output of the Data Rack. For more Info, read the Rack Case Tooltip.
block.witherutils.rackfluid_controller.d:
§9How to:§r
 This block is the Heart of the Data Rack. For more Info, read the Rack Case Tooltip.
block.witherutils.rackitem_controller.de:

 This block is the Heart of the Data Rack. For more Info, read the Rack Case Tooltip.

Resource.

Left Click on Mobs to save the MobName and Id.

item.witherutils.hammer.desc:
■-§9 §nInformation:
§r§fThe hammer is a versatile Tool. It offers three Functions that can prove useful in various situations.§r
■-§9 §nHowtoUse:
§r§fIn Combination with the WitherAnvil, you can process materials and create additional items. Also serve as a weapon against enemies. It can demolish blocks while recovering the recipe's materials. So, if you accidentally break misplaced blocks, you can reclaim the resources for reuse.§r
item.witherutils.remote.desc:
§9How to use:§r 
Allows you to wirelessly control a TV. To change the channel, simply right click in the direction of the TV. You can turn on/off the TV by sneaking instead.
